column4: NSLOCTEXT("[A4779ADE4B5C753C69647AAD90362785]", "F6FCCA874F19DC4211FF1998BA33B0FB", "I can\'t believe I was brain washed by him.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4779ADE4B5C753C69647AAD90362785]", "5E1C0FA7491B7CC7AD557FA568A19779", "He\'s strong. Can you defeat him? Why are you doing this?")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4779ADE4B5C753C69647AAD90362785]", "0075B95B44B7C368F4673BB438A775F7", "I\'ll fight for the island. Let\'s settle this now.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A4779ADE4B5C753C69647AAD90362785]", "BEF4E5694F4BF701D932C5988D665B99", "We don\'t want a ruler, you\'re our only hope.")
